However, the risk can be much higher for delivery workers who have to travel and interact with people.
Order Directly from the Restaurant, If PossibleIt is always better to order directly from the restaurant, as third-party apps can charge commission fees.
If You’re Using a Third-Party AppIf you have to order from an app but want to order ethically, pay attention to that particular service’s sick leave and benefits plan for their workers.
It will also provide two weeks of paid sick leave if an employee tests positive for COVID-19.
Instacart also allows all in-store shoppers to accrue sick leave.